She followed Black Aracnia into the transport.  


--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, JP3884@a... wrote:
>     Megatron inspected the vessle that rested before him. It would 
fit five, 
> and had medical capabilities, but no CR chamber. The front of the 
ship had 
> double cannons that would be used in defence, and on the two wings 
of the 
> vessle rested a missle turret. It was a fair craft, and Megatron 
was going to 
> use it on his ambassadorial missions.
>     "Adrax, Waspinator! Lets load up. Were going to go and see my 
old friend 
> Inferno and Rampage." He commanded in a bastardly voice.
>     Adrax spun around, in confusion. "Why there?" His multi-green 
eyes 
> narrowed.
>     Megatron's face fell in pure disgust, "Because....they are the 
key to the 
> complete allience of the Predacons and our victory over this planet 
and our 
> enemys!"
>     Waspinator giggled and buzzed inside the ship.
> 
>     Aracnia looked to Darkmouse and Quickstrike, "Get into the 
transport with 
> me. Were heading back to the ship."
